    # "She looks disappointed as she shuts the door and I walk back over to my house."
    "Ela parece desapontada ao fechar a porta e eu volto para minha casa."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:68
translate portuguese tvchatwithjamie_b827e096:

    # "She leads me to the living room, where the TV is paused on a show that I don't recognize."
    "Ela leva-me até à sala, onde a TV está em pausa num programa que eu não reconheço."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:69
translate portuguese tvchatwithjamie_1410557b:

    # gnd "I was just trying to finish up this series that I've been watching before school starts up again."
    gnd "Eu só estava a tentar terminar esta série que tenho visto antes das aulas recomeçarem."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:70
translate portuguese tvchatwithjamie_442eef5c:

    # pc "Cool. I barely watch any TV anymore."
    pc "Porreiro. Eu quase não vejo mais TV."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:71
translate portuguese tvchatwithjamie_e0203869:

    # gnd "Really? I love TV. I probably watch too much."
    gnd "A sério? Adoro televisão. Provavelmente vejo demasiada."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:73
translate portuguese tvchatwithjamie_5407ea16:

    # "We sit there for a few moments in an awkward silence. There are a couple times when Jamie seems like she wants to say something, but doesn't."
    "Ficamos ali sentados por alguns momentos num silêncio constrangedor. Há algumas vezes em que a Jamie parece querer dizer alguma coisa, mas não o faz."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:74
translate portuguese tvchatwithjamie_58b01cd5:

    # "It feels very strange, like she is uncomfortable with me for some reason. Like there is something between us."
    "Parece muito estranho, como se ela se sentisse desconfortável comigo por alguma razão. Como se houvesse algo entre nós."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:75
translate portuguese tvchatwithjamie_396a0d53:

    # "I have to break this silence with literally any conversation."
    "Tenho de quebrar este silêncio com qualquer conversa, seja ela qual for."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:76
translate portuguese tvchatwithjamie_1171aaad:

    # pc "Oh, I have a cell phone now."
    pc "Ah, agora tenho um telemóvel."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:78
translate portuguese tvchatwithjamie_5c1dfc7a:

    # gnd "Awesome, what's your number?"
    gnd "Fantástico, qual é o teu número?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:79
translate portuguese tvchatwithjamie_53b692f6:

    # "I tell her my new phone number and she puts it into her phone."
    "Digo-lhe o meu novo número de telemóvel e ela guarda-o no seu telemóvel."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:81
translate portuguese tvchatwithjamie_b9feb81a:

    # "Then she turns her phone around and holds it up to take a picture of herself."
    "Depois, vira o telemóvel e levanta-o para tirar uma foto de si própria."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:83
translate portuguese tvchatwithjamie_5ad0b0e8:

    # gnd "I sent you a text message, along with a picture of me so you can add me into your contacts, and we can chat whenever."
    gnd "Enviei-te uma mensagem, juntamente com uma foto minha, para que me possas adicionar aos teus contactos e possamos conversar quando quiseres."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:88
translate portuguese tvchatwithjamie_ea0a9e4e:

    # pc "I got it. I'll just add you to my contacts real quick."
    pc "Recebi. Vou adicionar-te aos meus contactos rapidinho."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:89
translate portuguese tvchatwithjamie_d7eecc80:

    # pc "And done."
    pc "E pronto."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:90
translate portuguese tvchatwithjamie_7a48c010:

    # gnd "Awesome."
    gnd "Fantástico."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:93
translate portuguese tvchatwithjamie_a06bb2fa:

    # pc "Great. I'll be sure to add you as soon as I get back home and get the phone set up."
    pc "Ótimo. Vou adicionar-te assim que chegar a casa e configurar o telemóvel."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:95
translate portuguese tvchatwithjamie_570f0e90:

    # "She sits on the couch next to me, leaning back against the arm rest to face me, her bare legs folded underneath her."
    "Ela senta-se no sofá ao meu lado, recostando-se no braço do sofá para ficar de frente para mim, com as pernas nuas cruzadas debaixo do corpo."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:96
translate portuguese tvchatwithjamie_06525d7f:

    # gnd "Do you want to watch my TV show with me?"
    gnd "Queres ver a minha série comigo?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:97
translate portuguese tvchatwithjamie_61f77a4c:

    # pc "Sure."
    pc "Claro."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:98
translate portuguese tvchatwithjamie_49f2ae65:

    # gnd "It's called The Nieces of Callahan. Have you ever watched any of it?"
    gnd "Chama-se «The Nieces of Callahan». Já viste algum episódio?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:99
translate portuguese tvchatwithjamie_c7fa5d68:

    # pc "Nope."
    pc "Não."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:100
translate portuguese tvchatwithjamie_f8a2b09a:

    # gnd "Well I'm sure you'll be completely lost, but I'll try to catch you up."
    gnd "Bem, tenho a certeza de que vais ficar completamente perdido, mas vou tentar pôr-te a par."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:102
translate portuguese tvchatwithjamie_fb6f3632:

    # "She plays the show, but talks pretty much the whole time through it, explaining which character was which, who was sleeping with who, and which characters she liked and hated."
    "Ela põe a série a passar, mas fala praticamente o tempo todo, explicando quem era cada personagem, quem andava a dormir com quem e quais as personagens de que gostava e detestava."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:103
translate portuguese tvchatwithjamie_8a51ccf8:

    # "The show doesn't interest me too much, but as we sit together, she moves closer and closer, until our sides are touching."
    "O programa não me interessa muito, mas, à medida que ficamos sentados juntos, ela aproxima-se cada vez mais, até que os nossos corpos se tocam."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:104
translate portuguese tvchatwithjamie_df180490:

    # "I think about putting an arm around her shoulder, but I'm not sure what she would think about it."
    "Penso em passar o braço pelos ombros dela, mas não tenho a certeza do que ela pensaria disso."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:105
translate portuguese tvchatwithjamie_02a91ff8:

    # "Still, being there next to her is nice."
    "Ainda assim, é bom estar ali ao lado dela."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:106
translate portuguese tvchatwithjamie_7c085331:

    # "Finally, the show ends."
    "Finalmente, o programa termina."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:108
translate portuguese tvchatwithjamie_616bf526:

    # gnd "Did you like it?"
    gnd "Gostaste?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:109
translate portuguese tvchatwithjamie_28b82c1c:

    # pc "Honestly, I couldn't really follow it, but what I saw was okay."
    pc "Sinceramente, não consegui acompanhar muito bem, mas o que vi foi bom."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:110
translate portuguese tvchatwithjamie_82d9fc6f:

    # gnd "Yeah, you kind of have to watch it from the beginning."
    gnd "Sim, é preciso ver desde o início."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:111
translate portuguese tvchatwithjamie_95fb6df8:

    # gnd "Thanks for sitting through it with me anyways. That was nice."
    gnd "Obrigada por teres ficado a ver comigo na mesma. Foi simpático da tua parte."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:112
translate portuguese tvchatwithjamie_4eb9bd3a:

    # pc "Yeah it was. I enjoyed it."
    pc "Sim, foi. Gostei."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:115
translate portuguese tvchatwithjamie_0bde0b2d:

    # gnd "I'm so glad you're back in town. I know we didn't hang out much before you left, but I've always liked you and thought about you."
    gnd "Estou tão contente por estares de volta à cidade. Sei que não saíamos muito antes de te ires embora, mas sempre gostei de ti e pensei em ti."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:116
translate portuguese tvchatwithjamie_48b6a79b:

    # pc "Yeah, we had some good times when we were younger."
    pc "Sim, passámos bons momentos quando éramos mais novos."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:117
translate portuguese tvchatwithjamie_234edbbb:

    # gnd "Yeah we did. I wish we would have stayed friends through high school. I made a lot of bad decisions then."
    gnd "Sim, tivemos. Quem me dera que tivéssemos continuado amigos durante o liceu. Tomei muitas decisões erradas naquela altura."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:118
translate portuguese tvchatwithjamie_ce0b88b7:

    # pc "I think we all did."
    pc "Acho que todos nós tomámos."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:119
translate portuguese tvchatwithjamie_ec3ba06e:

    # gnd "Ain't that the truth."
    gnd "É mesmo verdade."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:121
translate portuguese tvchatwithjamie_68579f4f:

    # "She smiles at me, and we stand awkwardly for a few moments."
    "Ela sorri para mim e ficamos ali, um pouco sem jeito, por alguns momentos."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:122
translate portuguese tvchatwithjamie_5a0cac5d:

    # pc "Anyways, I better get home."
    pc "De qualquer forma, é melhor ir para casa."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:124
translate portuguese tvchatwithjamie_792d2ec7:

    # gnd "Okay, well thanks for coming to see me. Stop by anytime or send me a text if you want to chat."
    gnd "Está bem, obrigado por teres vindo ver-me. Passa por cá quando quiseres ou manda-me uma mensagem se quiseres conversar."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:126
translate portuguese tvchatwithjamie_d41d8cd9:

    # voice "voices/jamie_007.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_007.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:127
translate portuguese tvchatwithjamie_598f8960:

    # gnd "See you later."
    gnd "Até logo."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:129
translate portuguese tvchatwithjamie_3608be46:

    # "She smiles and waves as I walk out the door, shutting it behind me, and walk over to my house."
    "Ela sorri e acena enquanto saio pela porta, fechando-a atrás de mim, e caminho até à minha casa."

